{"tid":441134,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"次次上youtube聽歌都......","createTime":"2017-10-19T11:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T11:38:18.000Z","uid":2719,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"860b8d8b905f495b4b1a7882c197ea6da43e664d","tid":441134,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:24:42.000Z","msg":"覺得好無奈<br />\n屌你啲時間洗唔洗過得咁快<br />\n好多以為岀咗無耐嘅歌<br />\n睇返發佈日期原來已經6,7年前<br />\n<br />\n連那些年都講緊就7年<br />\n係2011年嘅作品<br />\n<br />\n時光飛逝之快 我心態完全適應唔到<br />\n明明自己已經長大 朋友都有結婚生仔<br />\n但我仲覺得自己好年輕 <br />\n<br />\n唉 點解可以咁殘酷 救命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7520498dc468f375d4926950c747d2ebd1fc883f","tid":441134,"uid":4494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:30:02.000Z","msg":"細個覺得老豆老母成撚日聽埋啲8/90年代歌好out<br />\n依加到我成日聽埋啲90年代後同千禧年代既歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係我唔想去聽新既歌<br />\n只係新既歌已經搵唔返當年做學生聽緊嗰首歌既感覺<br />\n細個聽情歌 親情歌都不以為然<br />\n人大左 詮釋首歌又唔同左<br />\n有時諗返起學生時代都係聽呢啲歌<br />\n都咪話唔懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c3a228f4b1be2d064347b4064bc84a8500f113","tid":441134,"uid":71226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:30:59.000Z","msg":"2010 原來已經係咁耐之前嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e0d0861c48dabb09bc5ad757565d722b520b0e","tid":441134,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:38:18.000Z","msg":"其實毒撚一個更開心<br />\n愛與誠係2004年作品<br />\n咁就13,4年啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}